 What Where Find Jobs Advanced Job Search Chargeback Specialist - Remote US Seamless.AI 9 reviews Columbus, OH Remote Seamless.AI 9 reviews Read what people are saying about working here. Job details Job Type Full-time Full Job Description The Opportunity 
Seamless.AI is looking for a motivated, detail oriented, Chargeback Specialist to join our growing collections team! You will be provided with the training and guidance to help you succeed in this exciting opportunity! You will have the opportunity to use your relationship building and communication skills to successfully help us win disputes and assist with the collections on overdue accounts. Your expertise will directly impact the health of our company and even help in expanding the growth of our business. Join us and help share the best sales leads technology to change the lives of sales people around the world! 
Apply today if you have:
 At least 2 years of Chargeback & Disputes experience Some experience making Collection calls to customers High attention to detail
 Excellent verbal & written communication Thrive in a fast paced environment
 What you'll get to do everyday:
 Monitor customer accounts to track, identify & research any disputes on payments. 
Manage and reconcile open chargebacks and disputes.
 Partner with internal departments to maximize recovery and prevention of chargebacks.
 Investigate historical data for each debt, bill for disputes and collections.
 Find and contact customers to collect overdue payments by phone and email. 
Make proactive payment reminder calls and emails.
 Take actions to encourage timely overdue payments. 
Explain payment plan options and notify customers of any billing changes.
 Process payments as they are received. 
Resolve conflicts professionally. 
Update account status, document all conversations, record all dispute, chargeback, & collection efforts.
 Report on chargeback, dispute, and collection activity, while keeping management aware of escalated situations. 
